<item>
            <title>[LU-10187] Handle FID-in-dirent</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10187</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the ZFS backend is restored from MDT file-level backup, then the FID-in-dirent will be lost. It will strongly affect the performance for lookup/readdir. The namespace LFSCK should has the ability to rebuild/repair the lost/corrupted FID-in-dirent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
